---
import Layout from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Inguz Care — Residential Children’s Homes"
  description="Safe, nurturing homes with tailored support plans."
>
  <!-- HERO with background image -->
  <section class="relative pt-6 sm:pt-8 md:pt-10">
    <div class="relative h-[60vh] md:h-[70vh]">
      <img
        src="/hero.jpg"
        alt="Carer and children completing a colourful jigsaw puzzle together"
        class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
        loading="eager"
        fetchpriority="high"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 h-full flex items-center justify-center">
        <!-- centered on all screens -->
        <div class="text-white text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight max-w-[22ch] mx-auto">
            Welcome to INGUZ Care
          </h1>

          <p class="mt-6 text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl mx-auto max-w-[60ch]">
            A home built on warmth, belonging and growth.
          </p>

          <!-- Centered CTA buttons -->
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="w-full sm:w-auto text-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-[#5f7c7b] text-white font-semibold hover:bg-[#3d5756]"
            >
              Refer / Contact us
            </a>
            <a
              href="/our-homes"
              class="w-full sm:w-auto text-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-[#5f7c7b] text-[#5f7c7b] font-semibold hover:bg-[#eef5f4] bg-white/90"
            >
              Explore our homes
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INTRO / LANDING COPY -->
  <section class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-slate-900 space-y-4 text-left">
        <p>
          At INGUZ Care, we believe that every young person deserves to feel safe, valued and understood.
          Our home provides more than just care – it’s a space where relationships are nurtured, voices are
          heard, and every small step forward is celebrated.
        </p>
        <p>
          We create a family environment that encourages trust, self-expression and stability. Our approach
          is guided by therapeutic principles such as PACE (Playfulness, Acceptance, Curiosity and Empathy)
          and trauma-informed care – not as buzzwords, but as everyday practices in how we listen, respond
          and connect.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our team offers consistency, compassion and structure, helping each young person rediscover their
          strengths and build the confidence to move towards their future. Whether it’s sharing a meal,
          talking through emotions at the end of the day, or learning new ways to cope with challenges,
          we focus on moments that matter.
        </p>
        <p>
          We work closely with families, local authorities and therapeutic partners to ensure every child’s
          care journey is personalised and supported. You’re not just part of a service here – you’re part of
          a home that believes in your potential and your right to belong.
        </p>

        <!-- CENTRED PROMISE -->
        <div class="mt-10 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Our Promise</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            We listen. We reflect. We respond.
            <br />
            Because at INGUZ Care, change begins with connection.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR VALUES (expanded list) -->
  <section id="values" class="py-14">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center">Our Values</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-center text-slate-600">
        Our values shape everything we do — from how we recruit and train staff to how children and families
        experience our homes.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-center text-slate-600">Tap a value to read more.</p>

      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-6">
        <!-- Dignity & Respect -->
        <details class="rounded-xl border overflow-hidden">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-[#5f7c7b]"
          >
            <div class="aspect-square grid place-items-center text-center bg-[#5f7c7b] text-white px-3">
              <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold leading-tight">Dignity &amp; Respect</h3>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-4 space-y-2.5 text-sm">
            <p class="font-medium">
              Every child is valued as an individual with their own culture, identity and voice.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Compassion & Kindness -->
        <details class="rounded-xl border overflow-hidden">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-[#6f908f]"
          >
            <div class="aspect-square grid place-items-center text-center bg-[#6f908f] text-white px-3">
              <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold leading-tight">Compassion &amp; Kindness</h3>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-4 space-y-2.5 text-sm">
            <p class="font-medium">
              We care with empathy, patience and genuine warmth.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Safety & Stability -->
        <details class="rounded-xl border overflow-hidden">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-[#3d5756]"
          >
            <div class="aspect-square grid place-items-center text-center bg-[#3d5756] text-white px-3">
              <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold leading-tight">Safety &amp; Stability</h3>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-4 space-y-2.5 text-sm">
            <p class="font-medium">
              We build predictable routines and maintain strong safeguarding throughout.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Empowerment & Equality -->
        <details class="rounded-xl border overflow-hidden">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-[#88a7a6]"
          >
            <div class="aspect-square grid place-items-center text-center bg-[#88a7a6] text-white px-3">
              <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold leading-tight">Empowerment &amp; Equality</h3>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-4 space-y-2.5 text-sm">
            <p class="font-medium">
              We help children find their voice, build independence and access opportunity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Openness & Integrity -->
        <details class="rounded-xl border overflow-hidden">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-[#5f7c7b]"
          >
            <div class="aspect-square grid place-items-center text-center bg-[#5f7c7b] text-white px-3">
              <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold leading-tight">Openness &amp; Integrity</h3>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-4 space-y-2.5 text-sm">
            <p class="font-medium">
              We communicate honestly and take accountability for our practice.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Partnership & Collaboration -->
        <details class="rounded-xl border overflow-hidden">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-[#6f908f]"
          >
            <div class="aspect-square grid place-items-center text-center bg-[#6f908f] text-white px-3">
              <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold leading-tight">Partnership &amp; Collaboration</h3>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-4 space-y-2.5 text-sm">
            <p class="font-medium">
              We work closely with families, professionals and the wider community.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Growth & Development -->
        <details class="rounded-xl border overflow-hidden">
          <summary
            class="cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-[#3d5756]"
          >
            <div class="aspect-square grid place-items-center text-center bg-[#3d5756] text-white px-3">
              <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold leading-tight">Growth &amp; Development</h3>
            </div>
          </summary>
          <div class="p-4 space-y-2.5 text-sm">
            <p class="font-medium">
              We invest in the learning of both children and staff — growing stronger together.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION STATEMENT -->
  <section id="mission" class="py-14 bg-[#eef5f4]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <!-- Left: image -->
        <div>
          <img
            src="/logo.jpg"
            alt="Inguz Care — growth, development, success"
            class="w-full rounded-xl shadow object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Right: text (vertically centered) -->
        <div class="text-slate-900 md:pl-4">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Mission Statement</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            At Inguz Care, our mission is to provide a safe, nurturing home where young people are known as individuals
            and supported to thrive. With a broad, multi-disciplinary team and strong partners around us, we tailor
            trauma-informed, relationship-based support so every voice is heard, identity is celebrated, and the skills
            for independence grow day by day.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
